quran[59]{c,v,t}:
  44,1,"Haa, Miim"
  44,2,Mi woondirii Defere …ìanngunde nden
  44,3,"Men jippinirii nde e jemma barkinaa…óo, Men siforii wonde jertinoo…ìe"
  44,4,Ko e on (jemma) woni ko senndetee kala fiyaaku √±e√±aa…óo
  44,5,∆äum ko yamiroore immorde ka Amen. Men siforii wonde Nuloo…ìe
  44,6,"yurmeende immornde ka Joomi maa. Pellet, ko Kanko woni Nanoowo, Anndu…óo On"
  44,7,"Jey…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji, si wonii ko on yananaa…ìe"
  44,8,"Rewetee…óo goo alaa, si wanaa Kanko. Himo wuurna, Himo wara. Jey…óo on Jeyi baabiraa…ìe mon aram…ìe …ìen"
  44,9,"Ko woni tun, …ìe wonii e sikke, hi…ìe fija"
  44,10,Habbito √±alnde kammu ngun ardata e curki fee√±uuki
  44,11,"suddayki yim…ìe …ìen. [∆Åe wi'anee]: \"∆äum ko lepte muusu…óe"
  44,12,"Joomi amen, huncan men lepte …óen. Menen ko men gom…óim…ìe"
  44,13,"Ko honno …ìe waajitorta, ko goongo Nulaa…óo …ìanngin…óo ariino …ìe"
  44,14,"Refti …ìe hucciti, …ìe wi'i: \"Ko tinndinaa…óo, haangaa…óo"
  44,15,"Awa ko Men ittoo…ìe lepte …óen see…óa; kono pellet, ko on ruttitotoo…ìe"
  44,16,"√ëalnde Men nanngiroyta wippannde mawnde nden, pellet, ko Men yottoytoo…ìe"
  44,17,"Gom…óii Men jarribinoke ado ma…ì…ìe, yim…ìe Fir'awna …ìen, Nulaa…óo teddu…óo ari e ma…ì…ìe"
  44,18,"wonnde: \"Wa…óee e juu…óe am, jeyaa…ìe Allah …ìen. Min ko mi Nulaa…óo e mon, hoolnii…óo"
  44,19,"E wonde wata on townitano Allah, tawde mi addanay on hujja …ìanngu…óo"
  44,20,"Min kadi non, mi moolorii Jey…óo lam On Jeyi on, nde fi…óotonmi kaa∆¥e"
  44,21,"Si on gom…óinaa lam, haray selee lam"
  44,22,"O noddi Joomi makko, wonnde: \"∆Åee …óoo, ko yim…ìe bom…ìe"
  44,23,Yaadir e jeyaa…ìe Am …ìen jemma; anndon ko on cukketee…ìe
  44,24,"Accaa maayo ngon dee∆¥a [si on lummbii] …ìeya kan, ko konu yooleteengu"
  44,25,∆äuu…óii ko …ìe acci e gese e …ìulli
  44,26,e remuruuji e ko…óande teddunde
  44,27,e neemaaji …ói …ìe wonunoo e neeminireede
  44,28,Ko wano non. Hooti Men ronini …ói yim…ìe goo
  44,29,"Kammu ngun to…ìaali …ìe, wanaa leydi ndin, …ìe wonaali kadi mu√±antee…ìe"
  44,30,Gom…óii Men da…óndii …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen e lepte hoyneeje
  44,31,"immorde e Fir'awna, tawde o laatino townitii…óo, jeyaa…óo e fantim…ìe …ìen"
  44,32,Gom…óii Men su…ìorike …ìe e dow ganndal e hoore winndere nden
  44,33,"Men okki …ìe maandeeji, …ói jarrabuyee …ìanngu…óo woni e mun"
  44,34,∆Åee kan no wi'a
  44,35,"Ndee wonaali, si wanaa maayde amen aranere nden tun. Men wonatah immintinoytee…ìe"
  44,36,"Awa artiree baabiraa…ìe amen …ìen, si wonii ko on goongu…ìe"
  44,37,"Kere ko kam…ìe …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude kaa ko yim…ìe \"Tubba'in\" …ìen e …ìeya adinoo…ìe …ìe? Men halkuno …ìen, tawde hari ko …ìe bom…ìe"
  44,38,"Men tagiraali kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin e ko woni hakkunde majji kon, fijoo…ìe"
  44,39,"Men tagiraali …óin …ói…ói, si wanaa e goonga. Kono ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe anndaa"
  44,40,"Pellet, ko √ëalaande Senndindiro ngon, woni ko …ìe saatinanaa, kam…ìe fof"
  44,41,"√ëalnde nde gi…óo duncanoytaa gi…óo [mun] hay huunde; …ìe wonaali kadi walloytee…ìe"
  44,42,"si wanaa mo Allah yurmaa woo. Pellet, ko Kanko woni Foolu…óo, Hinnotoo…óo On"
  44,43,"Pellet, leggal Zaqquumi ngal"
  44,44,ko √±aametee bakkondim…ìe …ìen
  44,45,A sikkay ko taayinaa ; hino fata ka nder deedi
  44,46,Wano wul…óam fatirta
  44,47,Nanngee mo poo…óiron ka hakkunde dul…ìaynge
  44,48,"refti yuppon ka hoore makko, lepte fatinaa…óe …óen"
  44,49,"Mee…óu non ! An [sikkunoo…óo] ko a foolu…óo, teddu…óo"
  44,50,Awa ko …óum woni kon ko sikkiti…óon e mum
  44,51,"Pellet, gom…óu…ìe …ìen wonii e weerde hoolniinde"
  44,52,e nder gese e …ìulli
  44,53,"hi…ìe …ìoornoo ko …óaati e ko tekki, hara hi…ìe fewtondiri"
  44,54,Ko wano non. Men resini …ìe kadi yaaju…ìe gite
  44,55,"Hi…ìe nodda toon, kala muuyantee…ói, hara ko …ìe hoolii…ìe"
  44,56,"∆Åe mee…óataa ton maayde, si wanaa maayde aranere nden. O da…ónda …ìe lepte Jahiimi …óen"
  44,57,"ko dokkal non, immorde ka Joomi maa. Awa ko …óum woni maloore mawnde nden"
  44,58,"Ko Men newiniri nde e …óamngal maa…óa, ko no …ìe waajitora"
  44,59,Habiito. Kam…ìe ko …ìe habbitii…ìe